{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_11_02",
  "title": "井川葵",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影終了後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの、莉央との喧嘩の話？\n喧嘩した後、一体どうやって仲直りしたのかって？",
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.6389798482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "君からお茶に誘ってくるなんて、めずらしいと思ったら\n昔の話って、そんなに気になるものかなぁ",
      "startTime": 13.3983336593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺がリズノワを知った時にはもう\n葵と莉央さんは、固い絆で結ばれてたからな",
      "startTime": 19.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3057827949
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃなかった頃の話って言われたら\nやっぱり気になるんだよ",
      "startTime": 26.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、そういうもんか。まぁ、話してもいいけど\n莉央には絶対言わないでよ",
      "startTime": 33.5911789577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.0631295521
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.0631295521
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "最初に会った時の莉央は、なんかいろいろ気負っててさ\nピリピリしてるし、全然楽しそうじゃなかった",
      "startTime": 43.0578456243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.4215196291
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "でも一緒に踊ってみたら、なんて力強くて\n情熱的なステップなんだって思ったんだよね",
      "startTime": 50.3578456243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.0528347332
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.0528347332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "組むならこの人がいいって、自然と思ったんだよ\nそのはずだったんだけど、デビューしたらさ……",
      "startTime": 61.0911789577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワはデビュー直後から人気だったし\n仕事もトントン拍子って感じだったよな？",
      "startTime": 68.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.7857836086
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないよ。デビューしてすぐの頃は\n会場を埋められないこともあったし",
      "startTime": 75.3318137487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "僕は、莉央と二人で踊っていられれば良かったのに\nデビューした途端、みんながああしろこうしろって",
      "startTime": 81.7318137487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.9424503325
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "その莉央も、僕がファンサを全然しないとかどうとか\n毎日、僕にガミガミ怒ってたしね",
      "startTime": 90.7984804154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "昔の莉央を{user}君にも見せたかったよ\nまるっきり狂犬みたいだったんだから",
      "startTime": 97.0318137487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.7490716933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなに怖かったのか……\n確かに出会った頃の莉央さんは尖ってはいたけど",
      "startTime": 103.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.9024049121
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、だから僕も文句言うならそっちがやればって\n面倒なことは全部、莉央に任せちゃってたんだよね",
      "startTime": 111.8395005863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今の二人からは想像がつかないな……\nそれで、どうして大喧嘩になったんだ？",
      "startTime": 118.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9903182664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "あの喧嘩は……原因はなんだったかな\n莉央が原因だった気がする。うん、きっとそうだ",
      "startTime": 127.328434531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.3903412181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "確か、ワンマンライブの衣装がひらひらしてたから\n僕が意見を言ったんだ。あくまで的確なね",
      "startTime": 135.4951011976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "でも莉央は「アイドルだから当然」としか言わないし\nそれで、言い合いになっちゃった訳",
      "startTime": 143.1617678643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 147.0533344268
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 147.0533344268
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 147.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ、三枝さん？　そんなに慌ててどうしたのさ\n息も切らしてるし、運動不足なんじゃないの",
      "startTime": 153.728434531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-shj001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……こっちを走り回らせて、その言い草か\nそれより、莉央と喧嘩したんだって？",
      "startTime": 163.5617678643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 167.6117466925
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "……喧嘩じゃないよ、莉央が勝手に怒っただけ\nそれにどうせ、まだ僕に怒ってる",
      "startTime": 172.7617678643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "だから大人な僕は、莉央の頭が冷えて落ち着くまで\nここで踊って、有意義に時間を使ってるだけ",
      "startTime": 180.328434531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 183.9889802614
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-shj002.m4a",
      "text": "……莉央、葵を凄く心配してたぞ\n先に帰らせたが、さっきまで必死で探してたんだ",
      "startTime": 189.628434531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "莉央が、僕を心配して……？　……そっか\nそれは……僕も悪いことしちゃったな",
      "startTime": 203.1617678643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 207.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "それなら……うん、ほら、莉央も大人げないとこあるし\nここは大人な僕から、歩み寄るべきだよね",
      "startTime": 214.2284284275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "shj",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-shj003.m4a",
      "text": "はは。そう言っちまうところが\nまだまだ小学生だな",
      "startTime": 221.6284284275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-night",
      "startTime": 223.9276593367
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_11_02-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "莉央の家に行って来るから住所教えてよ。莉央、僕の\nことが心配で心配で倒れちゃってるかもしれないからね",
      "startTime": 228.7617617608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 233.5417186577
    },
    {
